Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, Mr. Mousey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you stay off that leg\Nand do everything I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will be just like new in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're welcome. Happy to be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You... found a watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You... wanna be a watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Running out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're... late?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late for a very important date!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The big brunch for Princess Celestia\Nat Sugarcube Corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Princess is here\Nin Ponyville for a party...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we all promised we'd be there.\NBut I'm not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do I look all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need to bring anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting! I'm missing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you hadn't reminded me,\NI might have not remembered and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I wouldn't be there and everypony\Nwould be wondering where I was and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay then. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what do I have to do to get to be\None of the Princess's royal guards, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the pay good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooo! Anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Too good. I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Halt!\N-Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No one. Never mind. I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, sirs. She's on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you could make it, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be the same without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How's everypony doing? Good? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else we can get for you, dearies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I-I mean, esteemed guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine, Mr. and Mrs. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late. I had to finish\Ntaking care of a patient first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you and your Tender Loving Care of little animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know Princess Celestia is gonna love that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hope she will...\NI mean, of course she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Twilight. I thought I was the only one\Nwho got nervous at social gatherings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not that. I just want the Princess\Nto approve of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's met us all before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And read about you in my letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the first time she spent any real time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everypony to make a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's just a casual get-together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the dress!\NCareful, you're gonna spill that on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, that looks delicious. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, does it stain?! Keep it away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... perhaps not that casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... which is the salad\Nand which is the appetizer again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And which am I supposed to eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Twilight. So our friends' manners aren't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt the Princess will even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookies, candies and pies! Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate Fountainy goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna eat that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand pardons, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite all right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty teacup at 4 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I see it, honey bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but of course, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you, dear? Fluttershy, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand from Twilight Sparkle's letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you enjoy tending\Nto the needs of woodland creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I love to take care of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As do I. As princess, I care deeply\Nabout all creatures, great and small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing means more to me\Nthan the well-being of all my subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Philomena, my pet. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do say hello to our gracious hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She is quite a sight, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, if I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everypony.\NI'm afraid I have to cut the party short.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has requested an audience with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal duty calls. Thank you for a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a joy getting to know you all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can eat someth'n! I'm starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay right where you are.\NAll I want is a clear path to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,NOBODY MOVE and my dress won't get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back! Back, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know for sure\Nhow things went with the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...but at least no big disasters happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you ever get in such bad condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Philomena.\NI'll nurse you back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As a favor to the Princess, who's obviously\Njust far too busy to care for you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Princess will appreciate the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. We'd better get you to bed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is far worse than I thought.\NWhat you need is some medicine. Stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Philomena.\NThis will fix you right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Fluttershy expected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Always works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Almost always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like home-made soup\Nto cure what ails you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now. You're not gonna get better\Nif you don't cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... See? It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good and good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here come the choo-choo train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chugga-chugga, chugga-chugga, whoo-whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Philomena.\NI know what'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right here. I have just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Philomena. I brought a fellow\Nfeathered friend by to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hummingway here was sick once too,\Nbut he let me help him and got better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to your new friend Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, look. I think he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn now, Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... good try?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what'll clear up that tickle in your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A humidifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that feeling now for you,\NPhilomena? Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know lots of other ways to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You're gonna get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aromatherapy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgical tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be easy\Nto nurse you back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at you. You're worse than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to drop by and\Nsay thank you so very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...for making such a good impression\Non the Princess today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Celestia's pet doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't leave the poor thing there.\NShe needed my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. NonononononoNO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I just walk away and not do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but... she doesn't belong to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Without telling anypony?!\NWithout asking permission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you had good intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you have got to return Princess's pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hurry, we can put her back\Nbefore anypony even realizes she's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told we could find Twilight Sparkle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We regret to inform you, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...that the royal pet has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You don't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that dry night air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, day air's even drier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You guards better be on your way\Nif you're gonna find the Princess's missing pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Philomena, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you ever so much for keeping me in the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,BYE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to return Philomena, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what the Princess is gonna do\Nif she finds you're the one who took her pet, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can't be anything good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She might banish you from Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or throw you in a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or banish you and then throw you in a dungeon\Nin the place that she banishes you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think the Princess would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Granted that probably won't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but do you wanna take any chances?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All that really matters to me is that\Npoor little Philomena here gets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very noble of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write to you when you're banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I'm banished too\Nsomewhere there's no post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have to write to me. Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Twilight. You just have to\Nhelp me get Philomena healthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then we can return her to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give her any kind of medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to, but she wouldn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to MAKE her take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be such a pushover, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to show this patient who's the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Make her straighten up and fly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Done. Okay, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... well, she keeps pulling her feathers off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that haven't fallen out yet\Nfrom all her coughing, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough love, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You want her to get well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Of course, but...\N-NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she desperately needs some bed rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I can't get her to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One step ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good, Philomena, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just relax and try to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this soup over here? Smells delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it for Philomena. But she wouldn't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she'll eat it, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Philomena! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?\NAre you having a race?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can I play? 123GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me!\N-Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Beg your pardon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry, but we've gotta find...\N-The Princess's pet bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Philomena! Come down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll hurt yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Princess. Fluttershy didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm the one who did it.\N-But you were only trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Some help I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will ya let me do this? She'll go easier on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for trying to protect me, Twilight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia, I'm the one who took your pet bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I really was only trying to help the poor little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I was gonna bring it back to you, honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you wanna banish me and then throw me\Nin a dungeon in the place that you banish me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...then that's what I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop fooling around, Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scaring everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing? What happened to Philomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's quite a sight, as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing unusual for a phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Philomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A... A phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A phoenix is a majestic and magical bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,While it appears healthy and happy\Nmost of the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...every so often it must renew itself by shedding\Nall of its feathers and bursting into flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather melodramatic, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It then rises from the ashes, fresh as a daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All just a normal part of the life cycle of a phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid, mischievous little Philomena here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...took the occasion to have\Na little fun with you, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're sorry, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So... aren't you gonna banish me?\NOr throw me in a dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or banish me and then throw me in a dungeon\Nin the place that you banish me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, my little pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on Earth would you get such an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have some imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy really did do everything she could\Nto try to take care of Philomena for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do appreciate that your heart\Nwas in the right place, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But all you had to do was ask me and\NI could have told you Philomena was a phoenix...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and saved you all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I shouldn't have jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll ask before\Ntaking matters into my own hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I write you a letter\Nabout that lesson, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's quite all right.\NI think I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Philomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
